        <title>Glosas pela música portuguesa @ Lusophonica</title>
        <description>&lt;p&gt;I’ve had the pleasure of putting together the second episode of &lt;em&gt;Glosas pela música portuguesa&lt;/em&gt;, a live radio show produced by &lt;a href=&quot;www.mpmp.pt&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;mpmp&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt; for &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.lusophonica.com/&quot;&gt;Lusophonica&lt;/a&gt;. Presented live out of their booth in Cascais, my set consisted of two hours of some of the most interesting music composed and improvised these last few years, as well as some hopefully delightful and enticing bridges to music that’s (let’s call it) a bit less contemporary.&lt;/p&gt;

